Package event

Interface EventInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<EventInterface>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AntMoveEvent, PheromoneEvaporationEvent, PrintEvent
    public interface EventInterface
extends java.lang.Comparable<EventInterface>
    Represents an interface for events in the simulation. Event classes implementing this interface should provide implementations for the executeEvent(), getEventTime(), and setNextEventTime() methods.
